SUB_W19_WRLD_AMYA_INITIAL_000_CUT_000_00.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_WRLD_AMYA_INITIAL_000_CUT_000_00.text:
Mmm, the air here is so fresh—and just
feel all that spirit energy! I bet I'm gonna
get some great mana from this world!

SUB_W19_WRLD_AMYA_INITIAL_000_CUT_000_01.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_WRLD_AMYA_INITIAL_000_CUT_000_01.text:
Just wish I could find someone to show
me around, but meh! I guess I'll go
look for my cat in the meantime.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_EAGLE_000_CUT_000_000.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_EAGLE_000_CUT_000_000.text:
Well, hello there, birdie!
Wanna be my guide in this world?

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_EAGLE_000_CUT_000_010.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_EAGLE_000_CUT_000_010.text:
Aw, what a sweetheart.
I'm gonna call you Eaglesby!

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_EAGLE_000_CUT_000_020.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_EAGLE_000_CUT_000_020.text:
Hm? You want me to hop on your back?
Hey, don't have to ask me twice!

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_EAGLE_000_CUT_010_000.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_EAGLE_000_CUT_010_000.text:
So this whole world exists on the
branches of a single tree, huh?

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_EAGLE_000_CUT_010_010.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_EAGLE_000_CUT_010_010.text:
Oh, I see an animal statue!
I wonder who made it.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_EAGLE_000_CUT_010_020.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_EAGLE_000_CUT_010_020.text:
Wow, there are lots of those animal statues.
...Wait, are you saying they're actually
PETRIFIED animals? Oh, that's terrible!
No wonder you wanted me to see this.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_EAGLE_000_CUT_020_000.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_EAGLE_000_CUT_020_000.text:
I bet you want me to save
all those animals, huh?

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_EAGLE_000_CUT_020_020.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_EAGLE_000_CUT_020_020.text:
Uh, what's this? Seeds, bugs, and a flute?
I bet this flute is to call you, right?

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_EAGLE_000_CUT_020_050.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_EAGLE_000_CUT_020_050.text: Eh, whatevs! I'll figure it out.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_EAGLE_000_CUT_020_080.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_EAGLE_000_CUT_020_080.text:
You want me to check out the vines?
I get you. Leave it to me.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_EAGLE_010_CUT_000_010.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_EAGLE_010_CUT_000_010.text:
Don't worry, Eaglesby.
I'll work this out.

SUB_W19_GIMK_AMYA_IVY_000_CUT_000_000.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_GIMK_AMYA_IVY_000_CUT_000_000.text: Looks like I can climb up these vines.

SUB_W19_GIMK_AMYA_IVY_000_CUT_010_000.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_GIMK_AMYA_IVY_000_CUT_010_000.text: So if I can use vines to go up...

SUB_W19_GIMK_AMYA_IVY_000_CUT_010_010.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_GIMK_AMYA_IVY_000_CUT_010_010.text: Can I also use them to go down?

SUB_W19_GIMK_AMYA_IVY_000_CUT_020_000.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_GIMK_AMYA_IVY_000_CUT_020_000.text:
Oh, look! The bugs I got earlier
are eating the vines!

SUB_W19_GIMK_AMYA_IVY_000_CUT_030_000.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_GIMK_AMYA_IVY_000_CUT_030_000.text:
The vines have turned
into a waterfall.

SUB_W19_GIMK_AMYA_IVY_000_CUT_030_010.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_GIMK_AMYA_IVY_000_CUT_030_010.text:
So I can ride currents down?
Talk about a fun way to get around!

SUB_W19_GIMK_AMYA_IVY_000_CUT_030_020.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_GIMK_AMYA_IVY_000_CUT_030_020.text:
So when I want to turn vines into a waterfall,
I use these bugs—which is great, because it
lets me save my magic for emergencies! Although I don't have many bugs either,
so I should probably be careful about
using them, too.

SUB_W19_GIMK_AMYA_IVY_000_CUT_030_030.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_GIMK_AMYA_IVY_000_CUT_030_030.text:
So I move up and down with vines and
waterfalls, but what do the seeds do?

SUB_W19_GIMK_AMYA_IVY_000_CUT_030_040.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_GIMK_AMYA_IVY_000_CUT_030_040.text:
Maybe they turn waterfalls into vines?
Yeah! I should try that!

SUB_W19_GIMK_AMYA_IVY_000_CUT_030_060.speaker: _NOT_SPECIFIED_
SUB_W19_GIMK_AMYA_IVY_000_CUT_030_060.text: Take a stick from the beaver's lodge!

SUB_W19_GIMK_AMYA_IVY_000_CUT_030_070.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_GIMK_AMYA_IVY_000_CUT_030_070.text:
Not sure what that voice was, but I feel
like this world is giving me a test!

SUB_W19_GIMK_AMYA_IVY_099_CUT_000_000.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_GIMK_AMYA_IVY_099_CUT_000_000.text:
I don't think this is where I'm
supposed to be right now.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_BEAVER_000_CUT_000_000.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_BEAVER_000_CUT_000_000.text:
Looks like you're the beaver, huh?
I'm gonna call you Beaverino!

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_BEAVER_000_CUT_000_010.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_BEAVER_000_CUT_000_010.text: May I have a stick please, Beaverino?

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_EAGLE_020_CUT_000_000.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_EAGLE_020_CUT_000_000.text:
Okay, I got a stick from Beaverino,
and my seed and bug games are strong.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_EAGLE_020_CUT_000_020.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_EAGLE_020_CUT_000_020.text:
So I guess now I go save
the petrified animals?

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_EAGLE_020_CUT_000_040.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_EAGLE_020_CUT_000_040.text:
Aw, you're not coming with me, Eaglesby?
Also, why don't you just fly me where I
need to go so I don't have to deal with
the bugs and vines and all that?

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_EAGLE_020_CUT_000_060.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_EAGLE_020_CUT_000_060.text:
...'Cause that would be cheating?
...And magic is ALSO cheating?
Aw, but we could save so much time!

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_EAGLE_020_CUT_000_080.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_EAGLE_020_CUT_000_080.text:
No, it's fine. Every world has its rules.
Oh, but last thing: Have you seen a cat
anywhere? I'm starting to worry it
might have been petrified.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_TURTLE_PUSHES_TREE_CUT.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_TURTLE_PUSHES_TREE_CUT.text:
Looks like Tommy Turtle gave
me a little of his magic!

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_TURTLE_PUSHES_TREE_CUT.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_TURTLE_PUSHES_TREE_CUT.text:
I bet I can topple trees like this now—
but there's only one way to know for sure!

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_BEAVER_CUTS_TREE_CUT_0.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_BEAVER_CUTS_TREE_CUT_0.text:
I wonder if there's any easy way for me to
take down this tree. I mean, I could set it
on fire, but that seems like a bad idea.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_BEAVER_CUTS_TREE_CUT_0.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_BEAVER_CUTS_TREE_CUT_0.text:
Aw, look! Beaverino is chewing
through its trunk! Perfect!

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_BEAVER_CUTS_TREE_CUT_0.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_BEAVER_CUTS_TREE_CUT_0.text:
That should be enough of an assist.
Stand back, guys! I've got this!

SUB_W19_FUNC_AMYA_CHANGE_CASCADE_TO_IVY_.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_FUNC_AMYA_CHANGE_CASCADE_TO_IVY_.text: I only have one seed left!

SUB_W19_FUNC_AMYA_CHANGE_CASCADE_TO_IVY_.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_FUNC_AMYA_CHANGE_CASCADE_TO_IVY_.text: Let's turn this waterfall into vines.

SUB_W19_FUNC_AMYA_CHANGE_IVY_TO_CASCADE_.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_FUNC_AMYA_CHANGE_IVY_TO_CASCADE_.text: I only have one bug left!

SUB_W19_FUNC_AMYA_CHANGE_IVY_TO_CASCADE_.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_FUNC_AMYA_CHANGE_IVY_TO_CASCADE_.text: Let's turn these vines into a waterfall.

SUB_W19_WRLD_AMYA_EAGLE_WHISTLE_CUT_000_.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_WRLD_AMYA_EAGLE_WHISTLE_CUT_000_.text: Okay, so that's where I'm at.

SUB_W19_WRLD_AMYA_EAGLE_WHISTLE_GAMEEND_.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_WRLD_AMYA_EAGLE_WHISTLE_GAMEEND_.text:
I'm so glad I was able to save
all the petrified animals.

SUB_W19_WRLD_AMYA_EAGLE_WHISTLE_GAMEEND_.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_WRLD_AMYA_EAGLE_WHISTLE_GAMEEND_.text:
Maybe I should look around
this world a bit more.

SUB_W19_FUNC_AMYA_ALL_GUARDIANS_SAVED_CU.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_FUNC_AMYA_ALL_GUARDIANS_SAVED_CU.text:
Looks like I was able to save
all the petrified animals.

SUB_W19_FUNC_AMYA_ALL_GUARDIANS_SAVED_CU.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_FUNC_AMYA_ALL_GUARDIANS_SAVED_CU.text: Now I just need my cat!

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_WORLDEXIT_000_CUT_000_.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_WORLDEXIT_000_CUT_000_.text:
Well, I found my cat,
so I guess I can move on?

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_WORLDEXIT_000_CUT_000_.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_WORLDEXIT_000_CUT_000_.text: No! I have to save them all!

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_WORLDEXIT_000_CUT_000_.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_WORLDEXIT_000_CUT_000_.text:
Sorry, guys, but I was just
here for my cat, sooo...

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_WORLDEXIT_000_CUT_000_.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_WORLDEXIT_000_CUT_000_.text: Byeee! Give my best to the others!

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GAMEEND_000_CUT_000_00.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GAMEEND_000_CUT_000_00.text: I saved all the animals, Eaglesby!

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GAMEEND_000_CUT_000_02.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GAMEEND_000_CUT_000_02.text:
Good thing I came here when I did, huh?
I mean, it would have been awful to just
leave all your animal friends as statues.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GAMEEND_000_CUT_000_03.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GAMEEND_000_CUT_000_03.text:
Anyway, I guess this is goodbye.
Take care, Eaglesby!

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GAMEEND_000_CUT_000_05.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GAMEEND_000_CUT_000_05.text:
You know, I never did find out how those
poor guys got petrified in the first place.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GAMEEND_100_CUT_000_05.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GAMEEND_100_CUT_000_05.text:
H-hey! What are you so 
ticked off about, Eaglesby!?

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GAMEEND_100_CUT_010_00.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GAMEEND_100_CUT_010_00.text:
Eaglesby got turned to stone!
Is this what happened to the others?

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GAMEEND_100_CUT_010_01.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GAMEEND_100_CUT_010_01.text: Oooh, I get it now! It's the job of the next traveler to save you, huh?

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GAMEEND_100_CUT_010_02.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GAMEEND_100_CUT_010_02.text:
The animals get petrified and freed, petrified
and freed... It's like this world is sustained
through its connection to others—and if my
theory is right, my part in this is done.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GAMEEND_100_CUT_010_03.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GAMEEND_100_CUT_010_03.text: Farewell to you all—and thank you.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GAMEEND_200_CUT_000_02.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GAMEEND_200_CUT_000_02.text: What are you so upset about, Bearzor?

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GAMEEND_200_CUT_000_04.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GAMEEND_200_CUT_000_04.text:
Get back, Squirrella!
I don't have any food for you!

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GAMEEND_200_CUT_000_08.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GAMEEND_200_CUT_000_08.text: Why, Tommy Turtle!? I saved your life!

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GAMEEND_200_CUT_000_10.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GAMEEND_200_CUT_000_10.text: Et tu, Eaglesby!? What's going on!?

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GAMEEND_200_CUT_010_00.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GAMEEND_200_CUT_010_00.text:
All the defeated animals turned to stone,
but what does that mean?

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GAMEEND_200_CUT_010_01.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GAMEEND_200_CUT_010_01.text:
I guess maybe it's another one of this
world's rules? Either way, as a witch,
it isn't my place to question why.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GAMEEND_300_CUT_000_02.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GAMEEND_300_CUT_000_02.text:
Why is everyone so upset with me!?
Should I not have saved you?

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GAMEEND_300_CUT_010_00.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GAMEEND_300_CUT_010_00.text:
Everyone's turned to stone...
Is it MY fault? I don't understand!
Explain it to me, Eaglesby!

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GAMEEND_300_CUT_010_01.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GAMEEND_300_CUT_010_01.text:
I'm sorry, but I guess I can't save everyone
after all. Well, hang in there and I'm sure
someone will come by to free you eventually.
But for now... Bye.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GUARDIAN_FOREST_04_STO.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GUARDIAN_FOREST_04_STO.text:
Looks like Squirrella here is about to bite
into something. Could someone have taken
whatever it was after she turned to stone?

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GUARDIAN_FOREST_04_STO.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GUARDIAN_FOREST_04_STO.text:
Uh, but bigger question:
What do squirrels eat, anyway?

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GUARDIAN_FOREST_07_STO.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GUARDIAN_FOREST_07_STO.text:
Wow, you're big! Twice as big as I am,
at least. I think I'm going to call you
Bearzor, if that's cool.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GUARDIAN_FOREST_07_STO.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GUARDIAN_FOREST_07_STO.text: Boy, just imagine how much force this guy would have behind him if he were moving again! Er, but how do I get him moving again?

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GUARDIAN_FOREST_07_STO.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GUARDIAN_FOREST_07_STO.text:
Huh. Looks like he's missing a few teeth.
I wonder if they fell out somewhere.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GUARDIAN_FOREST_07_CUT.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GUARDIAN_FOREST_07_CUT.text:
Hurray! I'm glad to see Bearzor
looking so full of life.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GUARDIAN_FOREST_07_CUT.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GUARDIAN_FOREST_07_CUT.text:
And it seems like he understands
I'm the one who saved him.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GUARDIAN_NEST_02_STONE.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GUARDIAN_NEST_02_STONE.text:
Is this a bat? It looks like one,
but he doesn't have any wings.
I wonder if someone took them.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GUARDIAN_NEST_02_STONE.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GUARDIAN_NEST_02_STONE.text:
Looks like he has a seed in his mouth.
Er, is that what bats eat?

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GUARDIAN_NEST_02_STONE.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GUARDIAN_NEST_02_STONE.text: Man, even the seed is stone.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GUARDIAN_NEST_02_STONE.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GUARDIAN_NEST_02_STONE.text:
Well, guess I'd better get
Batsy his wings back!

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GUARDIAN_NEST_02_CUT_0.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GUARDIAN_NEST_02_CUT_0.text:
It's so nice to see you with wings,
Batsy. Now you can fly again!

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GUARDIAN_NEST_02_CUT_0.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GUARDIAN_NEST_02_CUT_0.text:
Aw, thanks a million, Batsy!
I bet Squirrella will love this.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GUARDIAN_SWAMP_06_STON.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GUARDIAN_SWAMP_06_STON.text:
Howdy-do, Tommy Turtle! ...Hmm. No response. 
Doesn't look like my magic would work either.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GUARDIAN_SWAMP_06_STON.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GUARDIAN_SWAMP_06_STON.text:
Looks like Tommy Turtle is missing a piece
of his shell. Not sure if that has anything to
do with his being turned to stone, but if
I find that piece, I should bring it back.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GUARDIAN_SWAMP_06_CUT_.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GUARDIAN_SWAMP_06_CUT_.text:
Looks like Tommy Turtle is up
and full of beans again!

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GUARDIAN_SWAMP_06_CUT_.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GUARDIAN_SWAMP_06_CUT_.text:
Sure makes me happy to see
you moving around, friend.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GUARDIAN_SWAMP_06_CUT_.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GUARDIAN_SWAMP_06_CUT_.text:
...Hm? You want to thank me by offering
your strength? Well, I'm sure I can find
a way to make use of that!

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_SWAMP_01_ROUTE2_C.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_SWAMP_01_ROUTE2_C.text:
Man, what a huge frog! I wonder what
it eats that lets it grow so big?

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_SWAMP_01_ROUTE2_C.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_SWAMP_01_ROUTE2_C.text:
Oh, looks like he's about to eat
something... Is that a bat wing?

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_SWAMP_01_ROUTE2_C.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_SWAMP_01_ROUTE2_C.text:
Glad I could grab that before
it got swallowed up.

SUB_W19_FUNC_AMYA_PLAT_SWAMP_01_ROUTE2_A.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_FUNC_AMYA_PLAT_SWAMP_01_ROUTE2_A.text:
Man, what a huge frog! Looks like it
could gobble me down in one gulp.

SUB_W19_FUNC_AMYA_PLAT_SWAMP_01_ROUTE2_A.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_FUNC_AMYA_PLAT_SWAMP_01_ROUTE2_A.text: Gyaaa! He IS trying to gobble me!

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_SWAMP_02_CUT_000_.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_SWAMP_02_CUT_000_.text:
Wait, is this some sort of animal bone?
'Cause it seems to be just about the
same size as Bearzor's missing teeth.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_SWAMP_02_EARLY_CU.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_SWAMP_02_EARLY_CU.text:
Wait, is this some sort of animal bone?
Maybe I'll take that with me. You never
know when stuff might come in handy!

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_SWAMP_03_CUT_000_.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_SWAMP_03_CUT_000_.text:
Boy, Snikky Snake sure looks miffed
about something—but I'm not afraid!

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_SWAMP_03_CUT_010_.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_SWAMP_03_CUT_010_.text:
Er, are snake eggs really this big?
Because those look a lot more like
bird eggs to me.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_SWAMP_03_CUT_010_.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_SWAMP_03_CUT_010_.text:
Well, I didn't plan on being an egg thief,
but as long as I am here, might as well!

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_SWAMP_04_CUT_000_.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_SWAMP_04_CUT_000_.text:
Boy, Crockles there sure looks miffed
about something—but I'm not afraid!

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_SWAMP_04_CUT_000_.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_SWAMP_04_CUT_000_.text:
Oh, looks like he's about to eat
something... Is that a bat wing?

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_SWAMP_04_CUT_000_.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_SWAMP_04_CUT_000_.text:
Glad I could grab that before
it got swallowed up.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_SWAMP_05_ROUTE2_C.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_SWAMP_05_ROUTE2_C.text:
Is the beaver building a house?
Aw, and look at his adorable waddle!
Hee hee hee! I can't even.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_SWAMP_05_ROUTE2_C.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_SWAMP_05_ROUTE2_C.text:
Uh-oh! My buddy Beaverino's in trouble!
I gotta save him!

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_SWAMP_05_ROUTE2_C.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_SWAMP_05_ROUTE2_C.text:
I mean, what was I gonna do?
Watch him get murdered as
I ponder the circle of life?

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_SWAMP_05_ROUTE2_C.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_SWAMP_05_ROUTE2_C.text:
What's up, Beaverino? You wanna give me
a present for saving you? Aw, thanks.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_SWAMP_06_ROUTE2_C.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_SWAMP_06_ROUTE2_C.text: Wow, that is one huge bug!

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_SWAMP_06_ROUTE2_C.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_SWAMP_06_ROUTE2_C.text:
Doesn't look like it's going to attack,
but its eyes are plenty bright, so I
sure don't want it looking my way.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_SWAMP_06_ROUTE2_E.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_SWAMP_06_ROUTE2_E.text:
Hey! Stop fighting, you two!
Get off each other and make nice!

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_SWAMP_06_ROUTE2_E.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_SWAMP_06_ROUTE2_E.text:
Aw look. They're flying away together.
I'm a peacemaker!

SUB_W19_FUNC_AMYA_PLAT_NEST_01_AUTO_CUT_.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_FUNC_AMYA_PLAT_NEST_01_AUTO_CUT_.text:
Never seen a spider that big before!
I better sneak past nice and quiet...

SUB_W19_FUNC_AMYA_PLAT_NEST_01_AUTO_CUT_.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_FUNC_AMYA_PLAT_NEST_01_AUTO_CUT_.text:
No way, man! I'm not gonna
end up as spider food today!

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_NEST_03_CUT_000_0.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_NEST_03_CUT_000_0.text:
Okay, I finally made it to the anthill.
You sure went on quite the adventure,
didn't you, Antsil?

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_NEST_03_ROUTE2_CU.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_NEST_03_ROUTE2_CU.text:
It looks like there's a seed in that anthill.
I wonder if they nabbed it from Squirrella.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_NEST_03_ROUTE2_CU.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_NEST_03_ROUTE2_CU.text:
I don't want to upset any of the ants,
so I'll just reach over reeeal slow...

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_NEST_03_ROUTE2_CU.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_NEST_03_ROUTE2_CU.text:
Got it! Now let's get
the heck outta here.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_NEST_04_CUT_000_0.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_NEST_04_CUT_000_0.text: Huh? What's an ant doing up here?

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_NEST_04_CUT_000_0.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_NEST_04_CUT_000_0.text:
Do you want me to take you somewhere?
Back to your anthill, I bet. Sure thing!

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_NEST_04_CUT_000_0.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_NEST_04_CUT_000_0.text:
Also, I'm gonna call you Antsil.
Now c'mon, Antsil!

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_NEST_04_ROUTE2_CU.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_NEST_04_ROUTE2_CU.text: The ants in this world sure are big!

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_NEST_04_ROUTE2_CU.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_NEST_04_ROUTE2_CU.text:
Looks like they're carrying some sort
of seed. If I follow them to their hill,
I might find some food for Squirrella.

SUB_W19_FUNC_AMYA_PLAT_NEST_05_AUTO_CUT_.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_FUNC_AMYA_PLAT_NEST_05_AUTO_CUT_.text: Man, that is one big beehive.

SUB_W19_FUNC_AMYA_PLAT_NEST_05_AUTO_CUT_.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_FUNC_AMYA_PLAT_NEST_05_AUTO_CUT_.text:
I was only looking at your house, bees!
You don't need to get so mad about it!

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_NEST_05_ROUTE2_CU.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_NEST_05_ROUTE2_CU.text:
A bug came out of the hive.
Looks like it's being chased.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_NEST_05_ROUTE2_CU.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_NEST_05_ROUTE2_CU.text:
Wow, that was close. Are you trying to
get to the swamp? If so, I'll take you.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_NEST_06_CUT_000_0.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_NEST_06_CUT_000_0.text:
There's something stuck on that web...
Hey, it's a bat wing!

SUB_W19_FUNC_AMYA_PLAT_NEST_06_ROUTE2_AU.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_FUNC_AMYA_PLAT_NEST_06_ROUTE2_AU.text:
A bug got caught in the spiderweb
and now it's gonna get eaten!

SUB_W19_FUNC_AMYA_PLAT_NEST_06_ROUTE2_AU.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_FUNC_AMYA_PLAT_NEST_06_ROUTE2_AU.text:
Phew! That was a close one.
You need to be more careful!

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_01_CUT_000.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_01_CUT_000.text: Aw, the wolf puppies are playing!

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_01_CUT_000.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_01_CUT_000.text:
Uh, hang on. I think they're
playing with a piece of shell.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_01_CUT_000.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_01_CUT_000.text:
Yeah, I better take that.
Could be important.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_01_CUT_000.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_01_CUT_000.text:
Hopefully this piece of shell will
let me unpetrify that turtle.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_02_ROUTE2_.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_02_ROUTE2_.text:
There could be an important item
in this cave. Let's take a look!

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_02_ROUTE2_.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_02_ROUTE2_.text: Huh? What's that shiny thing there?

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_02_ROUTE2_.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_02_ROUTE2_.text:
Are these Bearzor's fangs? Oh, yay!
I'll hold on to these.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_02_ROUTE2_.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_02_ROUTE2_.text:
It doesn't look like there's
anything in this cave...

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_02_ROUTE2_.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_02_ROUTE2_.text: Yep! Just a boring old cave.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_02_ROUTE2_.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_02_ROUTE2_.text:
The only thing in
this cave is fiends!

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_02_ROUTE2_.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_02_ROUTE2_.text:
Dang, this cave sucks.
Let's get outta here.

SUB_W19_FUNC_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_03_AUTO_CU.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_FUNC_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_03_AUTO_CU.text:
What the heck is that? It looks more like
an animal than a plant—and that part there
looks like a giant mouth.

SUB_W19_FUNC_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_03_AUTO_CU.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_FUNC_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_03_AUTO_CU.text:
It looks like insects are that
plant's favorite food.

SUB_W19_FUNC_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_03_AUTO_CU.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_FUNC_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_03_AUTO_CU.text:
I'd better be careful about walking
around here with any bug friends.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_03_ROUTE2_.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_03_ROUTE2_.text:
Man, that plant looks like it'll snap me
right up if I get anywhere close to it.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_03_ROUTE2_.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_03_ROUTE2_.text:
There's something in its mouth, but I can't
tell what it is unless I get closer.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_03_ROUTE2_.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_03_ROUTE2_.text:
Okay, I am NOT gonna end up
in the gullet of some plant!
...Also, do plants have gullets?
...Also also, what's a gullet?

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_03_ROUTE2_.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_03_ROUTE2_.text:
It's a piece of shell. Neat!
Better bring this back to Tommy Turtle.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_03_ROUTE2_.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_03_ROUTE2_.text:
Huh. Looks like some kind of shell?
Well, might as well hang onto it.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_04_CUT_000.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_04_CUT_000.text:
It's a bird's nest with brown feathers
around it. Looks like the owners are away.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_04_CUT_000.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_04_CUT_000.text:
Uh, and is this a snake skin?
What's it doing here?

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_04_EGGS_CU.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_04_EGGS_CU.text:
There we go—although I don't feel good
about just abandoning the eggs here.
I mean, what if Snikky Snake comes back?

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_04_EGGS_CU.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_04_EGGS_CU.text: I should go find mama or papa bird.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_04_CUCKOO_.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_04_CUCKOO_.text:
There you go! Home sweet home
for you and your...

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_04_CUCKOO_.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_04_CUCKOO_.text: Ack! Stop! What are you doing!?

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_04_CUCKOO_.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_04_CUCKOO_.text:
It pushed all the eggs out of its nest!
Does that mean I got the wrong one?

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_04_CUCKOO_.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_04_CUCKOO_.text: And after all that hassle, too! Nuts.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_04_OWL_CUT.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_04_OWL_CUT.text: Awww, look how happy she is!

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_04_OWL_CUT.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_04_OWL_CUT.text:
I should probably go; I don't want
to interrupt a family moment.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_05_CUT_000.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_05_CUT_000.text:
I wonder if those eggs and that
nest belong to this bird.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_05_CUT_000.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_05_CUT_000.text:
She seems pretty amped about something.
Maybe it's the missing eggs?

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_05_CUT_000.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_05_CUT_000.text: Also, her plumage is grey and white.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_05_CUT_000.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_05_CUT_000.text: Should I lead her back to the nest?

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_06_CUT_000.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_06_CUT_000.text:
Aw, that poor bird looks so sad.
Maybe she's worried about her eggs.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_06_CUT_000.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_06_CUT_000.text: Also, her plumage is brown and beige.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_07_ROUTE2_.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_07_ROUTE2_.text:
Man, that deer is way mad!
Better keep my distance.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_07_ROUTE2_.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_07_ROUTE2_.text:
Also looks like he has something dangling
from an antler? ...Oh! It's a bat wing!

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_07_ROUTE2_.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_07_ROUTE2_.text: Okay, got myself a bat wing!

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_07_ROUTE2_.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_07_ROUTE2_.text:
But bats have two wings,
so I still need one more.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_07_ROUTE2_.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_FOREST_07_ROUTE2_.text:
I've got both bat wings now.
Let's get these back to Batsy!

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_NEKO_000_CUT_000_000.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_NEKO_000_CUT_000_000.text:
My kitty! Oh, I'm so glad you
haven't been turned to stone!

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GUARDIAN_FOREST_04_EAR.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_GUARDIAN_FOREST_04_EAR.text:
Here's the walnut I just found.
It's all yours!

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_NEST_03_ROUTE2_EA.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_NEST_03_ROUTE2_EA.text:
There's a walnut in that anthill. It might
make for a good meal for someone.

SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_NEST_04_ROUTE2_EA.speaker: Ameya_Aisling
SUB_W19_EVAR_AMYA_PLAT_NEST_04_ROUTE2_EA.text:
Looks like it's carrying some kind of seed.
I bet I'll be able to find all sorts of seeds
if I check out its anthill.
